        <abstract>
            <p>Agrees with JDH on G. J. Allman’s work. Approves of JDH’s text proposing GJA for Royal Medal.</p>
            <p>Will be proud to see General Richard Strachey at Down – a truly great man.</p> 
<p>Specimens of <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi> are waiting to be examined.</p> 
        </abstract>
